00:13:27,912 --> 00:13:30,373
they get to feel this change as they move around.

256
00:13:30,894 --> 00:13:32,995
So we tapped into the contrast of nature versus man,

257
00:13:33,375 --> 00:13:36,777
land versus sea, reason versus myth, beauty versus war,

