00:14:32,209 --> 00:14:34,510
One of the key core philosophies of the actual world itself

282
00:14:34,590 --> 00:14:35,971
was the idea of honeycomb.

283
00:14:36,111 --> 00:14:37,973
So the notion of honeycomb actually

284
00:14:38,293 --> 00:14:40,634
copies quite significantly the way

285
00:14:40,675 --> 00:14:42,956
the ancient Greeks used to own their landscape, which

286
00:14:43,016 --> 00:14:44,937
is different city states would actually

287
00:14:45,058 --> 00:14:47,379
utilize the land between different mountain ranges.

288
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:52,602
