different regions as a separate space. We could change the thematic, we could change

292
00:15:03,347 --> 00:15:07,930
the type of people, the type of work that you'd see going on in the different regions

293
00:15:08,310 --> 00:15:11,831
based on this honeycomb building mountain ranges between the different areas.

294
00:15:12,212 --> 00:15:13,572
So the player as they're adventuring,

295
00:15:13,592 --> 00:15:14,573
they'd climb up a mountain

296
00:15:14,633 --> 00:15:16,353
and they get a cool view of the next vista,

297
