00:34:31,425 --> 00:34:33,506
allow us to create the numerous statues

695
00:34:33,526 --> 00:34:34,306
that you see in the world.

696
00:34:34,667 --> 00:34:36,647
There's thousands and thousands of different iterations

697
00:34:36,708 --> 00:34:39,749
of the statues, and basically it was built on the same system.

698
00:34:39,809 --> 00:34:42,671
Lego kit statues that could plug into each other,

699
00:34:42,751 --> 00:34:44,411
all with logic and data to make sure

700
00:34:44,431 --> 00:34:46,272
you couldn't do wacky different poses.

701
00:34:46,773 --> 00:34:48,694
And we also used the same system for the market

702
00:34:48,734 --> 00:34:50,254
so that we could allow the level artists

