00:39:09,364 --> 00:39:11,185
checking it from every angle like they like to do

791
00:39:11,646 --> 00:39:12,847
and making sure it's perfect.

792
00:39:13,207 --> 00:39:15,169
At the same time, the level designers are making sure

793
00:39:15,209 --> 00:39:16,991
that all of the NPCs have got everything they need

794
00:39:17,011 --> 00:39:18,232
to fulfill their actions,

795
00:39:18,372 --> 00:39:19,673
make sure that if you attack a fort,

796
00:39:19,693 --> 00:39:21,435
they've got all the weapons they need to attack you.

797
00:39:21,936 --> 00:39:26,081
make sure they've got places that they can go and sleep and go and eat without leaving the fort undefended,

798
00:39:26,182 --> 00:39:27,543
which did happen at one point.

799
00:39:28,124 --> 00:39:32,811
And we're getting to the point now where we're making a world that's starting to feel like it's ready to be played.

800
00:40:02,605 --> 00:40:03,926
So it's nearly the end, guys.

801
00:40:04,927 --> 00:40:07,749
So by remaining true to our vision, focus, and discipline

802
00:40:07,789 --> 00:40:09,650
in how we worked, trusting in each other,

