00:40:13,733 --> 00:40:15,855
while keeping the game engaged and empowered

805
00:40:16,295 --> 00:40:17,476
without any major scope.

806
00:40:18,276 --> 00:40:20,138
And then building at the same time the foundation

807
00:40:20,178 --> 00:40:22,379
that was for a game that was critically acclaimed.

