00:40:26,649 --> 00:40:30,433
Everything to this production is that we started to do our own work.

810
00:40:30,613 --> 00:40:31,694
We gathered the knowledge.

811
00:40:32,095 --> 00:40:33,336
We didn't rush in production.

812
00:40:33,376 --> 00:40:36,279
We took the time to get to know about what was ancient Greece.

813
00:40:36,599 --> 00:40:38,982
We studied so much, and not only at the beginning,

814
00:40:39,022 --> 00:40:40,143
but throughout the whole production.

815
00:40:40,183 --> 00:40:43,206
And even today, we still think we can learn about ancient Greece.

816
00:40:44,310 --> 00:40:50,613
Essential to the to the products as well was the team engagement and empowerment by giving product ownership to the experts. We

817
00:40:50,653 --> 00:40:55,955
were able to tap into their their knowledge and expertise to allow them to control their own vision control their own

818
00:40:55,995 --> 00:41:02,798
quality control their own backlog and really build upon their own department which were filtering down into the quality that we

819
00:41:02,838 --> 00:41:03,318
ended up with.

