00:41:03,979 --> 00:41:06,120
On top of that, the world phases by sticking to that.

821
00:41:06,200 --> 00:41:07,861
We rigidly fought for that to make sure

822
00:41:07,881 --> 00:41:09,822
that we could continuously build the world up

823
00:41:09,862 --> 00:41:11,744
in these different layers from beginning to end

824
00:41:11,804 --> 00:41:13,945
to make sure that we could continuously

825
00:41:13,985 --> 00:41:16,467
make empowered decisions as we worked.

826
00:41:16,787 --> 00:41:18,868
Yes, and the integration of Substance Designer

827
00:41:18,908 --> 00:41:21,250
